VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:UserDefaults\.standard|NSUserDefaults\s+standardUserDefaults)
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:UserDefaults.*(?:password|token|secret|key|credential|auth)|set\s*\(\s*\w+\s*,\s*forKey:\s*"(?:password|token|secret|key|auth) && MISSING:Keychain|CryptoKit|encrypt|SecItem
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects UserDefaults storage usage which may be inappropriate for secrets.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for UserDefaults Used for Sensitive Data.
